    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"long_descriptions_container\"></div></div><div class=\"qti-layout-row\"> <div class=\"qti-layout-col12\"> <div class=\"prompt\"> <div class=\"standalone_image qti-align-center\"><img alt=\"Graph of a triangle in the x y plane with the origin labeled O. Refer to long description.\" aria-describedby=\"LDC-BLL000001_01\" src=\"/images/d078dba1b37bdebc8bf17ecb0d91b4df.svg\"><div aria-label=\"Long description for triangle in the coordinate plane\" class=\"sr-only qti-visually-hidden\" id=\"LDC-BLL000001_01\" role=\"region\">\n<p class=\"dap_body\">The x axis ranges from negative 2 to 7 in increments of 1. The y axis ranges from 0 to 7 in increments of 1.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Vertex A of the triangle is at (4 comma 5).</li>\n<li>Vertex B of the triangle is at (negative 1 comma 4).</li>\n<li>Vertex C of the triangle is at (5 comma 3).</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div><p class=\"dap_body\">A triangle with vertices&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"A\"><math alttext=\"A\"><mi>A</mi></math></span>,&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"B\"><math alttext=\"B\"><mi>B</mi></math></span>, and&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"C\"><math alttext=\"C\"><mi>C</mi></math></span>&nbsp;is given in the&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"x y\"><math alttext=\"x y\"><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi></math></span>-plane. The vertices can be expressed as a&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"2 by 3\"><math alttext=\"2 by 3\"><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>3</mn></math></span>&nbsp;matrix of column vectors. The mapping of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"open angle brackets x comma y close angle brackets\"><math alttext=\"open angle brackets x comma y close angle brackets\"><mfenced close=\">\" open=\"<\"><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfenced></math></span>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"open angle brackets negative x comma negative y close angle brackets\"><math alttext=\"open angle brackets negative x comma negative y close angle brackets\"><mfenced close=\">\" open=\"<\"><mrow><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>-</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfenced></math></span>&nbsp;maps the vertices of the triangle so that the image of the transformation is a rotation of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"pi\"><math alttext=\"pi\"><mi>π</mi></math></span>&nbsp;radians counterclockwise about the origin. Which of the following gives the image vertices as a matrix of column vectors?</p> </div> </div> </div>\n",
